# Plan: Laser Layout — Nesting Optimizer for Laser Cutting

**Created**: 2026-03-26
**Branch**: main
**Status**: approved

## Goal

Build a Svelte web application that imports LightBurn (.lbrn/.lbrn2) and SVG files, extracts part outlines, and optimizes their placement on a configurable material sheet to minimize waste. Users can set part quantities, configure kerf spacing, preview the nested layout visually, and export the result as SVG or LightBurn format.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Parses SVG files and extracts part outlines as polygons
- [ ] Parses LightBurn (.lbrn/.lbrn2) XML files and extracts part outlines as polygons
- [ ] User can configure material sheet width and height (mm)
- [ ] User can set quantity per imported part
- [ ] Kerf/spacing is configurable with 0mm default
- [ ] Nesting algorithm places parts optimally with free rotation
- [ ] Visual preview renders nested layout on an SVG canvas
- [ ] Export to SVG format
- [ ] Export to LightBurn format

